// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-1191 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 511288ed-8459-5e0d-a26d-af99b936757b

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
